results.description: I was at the Copenhagen Zoo that day walking by the aquarium looking for this bear (I’d never seen one before). It wasn’t where it was supposed to be and I was about to leave thinking that it was sleeping or something and somehow it appeared above me standing on the crystal of the aquarium tunnel. I fell instantly in love with the perspective that I had and pick up my phone quickly  and took some shots before it moved. I’m glad I thought fast because it was there just for like 5-6 seconds. It made me feel very happy for the moment I was living. Sorry for my unperfect english, I’m mexican haha.
